				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">No, don't become a mage.... yes, you can solo for awhile, BUT, you can solo for MUCH longer with a necro.
<br />

<br />

<br />
My necro just dinged 26 last night, and I'm having more fun with him than I had with my mage.  Looking forward to the root/rot technique too.... just to test it out.   But being able to snare mobs is SUCH a godsend... AND if I bite off more than I can chew, send pet and FD...  Much better than send pet only to have it eaten up and then the mob follow you until you hit a zoneline
<br />

<br />

<br />
All in all, Necros have it MUCH better off.....<br />_________________<br /><span style="text-decoration: underline">**Proud Beta Tester for Lineage II**</span>
