				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Chenchi wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">I just joined the emersive world of EverQuest last night. I started as a ranger because, honestly, there were so many choices that I did not know what to do! Anyhow, I really like the idea of mages and I am just wondering if this is something that is enjoyable to do and works? 
