				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If you want to have the power to send something to hell very fast a mage is the best option. Our burst damage is very nice, as is our sustained damage. Until you hit elemental+ (which most will not) playing a mage kicks ass. Though not very important we can generally kick most any other classes ass in a duel. 
<br />
Step one-send pet in (air if your against a caster, earth for tanks)
<br />
Step two- Host of the elements... can't escape the wrath of the almighty army of superturds...
<br />
Step three- Servant of ro! Can't run away from SoR, so you either take the full damage and ignore or kill it (and therefore stand still enough for host and pet and mages nukes to send you to hell)
<br />

<br />
Of course this is all theory, if your a shitty mage you wont win against anyone.<br />_________________<br />Quote of the day- "If you are going to do something wrong at least enjoy it." -Leo Rosten
<br />

<br />

<br />
Save a tree, eat a beaver.
<br />
Level 65 beaver eating mage of Erollisi Marr.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
