			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Listen to Mart.  Make a necro.  The power that goes along with their flexibility is pretty undisputed and they are a pet class.
<br />

<br />
You get to FD to save your butt.  Rez yourself or group members.  Heal yourself and group members (group heal limited but nice).  Regen mana for yourself better than any other class.  Snare and solo better than any other class.  PUt out nasty damage, especially at higher levels.    They really have no weakness.
<br />

<br />
Go to the Test server and buff a character up to 25 by typing /testbuff and try out several character and see what you think.  This can be a little deceiving since some classes don't come into their own until a bit later, like shaman, but you'll get a decent flavor for it.<br />_________________<br />Sage Sarridon Soulcraver
<br />
Arch Convoker-Terris Thule</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
