				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">You should play whatever you want to play.  If you are out for phat lewt and pretty sparklies, you might want to choose another class.  I have many toons 50+ and a couple at 65 (between my wife and myself).  I always go back to the mage after a short time.  It just fits my style.
<br />

<br />
Being a mage is easy.  Being a good, productive group member as a mage is hard work.  I choose the latter.
<br />

<br />
Just experiment and do whatever makes you happiest.  Thats all that counts.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
